Detailed Description

container for data passed to a module - allows data to extracted sequentially like a input stream.

Object is a handle which refers to a sbwDataBlockReader which does the real work. This means that assignment between DataBlockReader objects simply creates a new handle refering to the same data. These references share the same cursor into the data as well.
